{"tid":1826923,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實勇武害死左場運動","createTime":"2020-01-16T13:54:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T20:49:30.000Z","uid":57220,"like":15,"dislike":413,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"0639591a8d8142ba53cad29aa4cdf2ff73eaf325","tid":1826923,"uid":57220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T13:54:22.000Z","msg":"當時冇火魔個類嘢<br />\n都唔會玩電槍<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"4753d4306e951da47783fbec6718b4cd1f927323","tid":1826923,"uid":198590,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T13:54:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\">「分化撚」勇武又分，廣告界擺工又分，理大又分。希望大家係檢討而唔係指責</span><br />\n會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#57220 - 蕉皮</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請大家保持批判性思考，善用不推文回覆，該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>屠龍小隊原來有槍 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>不過冇開過<br />\n龍鳩毛都未跌一條就柒左</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1775037/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1775037/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>其實勇武出黎做乜柒？識反省未 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>一個二個爭住出黎柒<br />\n今日係和平示威又掉哂戲油彈 <br />\n有咩作用先？你話你行出黎 一個頂十個就話<br />\n又唔係 剩係識鳩黎唔用腦<br />\n又唔聽人勸<br />\n鳩鳩下 仆街</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1774539/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1774539/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>請全部手足聽住 如果唔係廣告界既罷工 香港唔會走到呢一步 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>搞到香港鬼死咁亂 都不突止<br />\n仲要掉器油彈 諗住過左區選就肯收手<br />\n點知<br />\n又搞個廣告班鬼頭仔搞罷工 搞死香港<br />\n希望大家咪再同佢地癲 <br />\n感謝！</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1772605/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1772605/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>理工班人係咪戇鳩 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>磨爛蓆，一早出黎就唔撚死咁多手足啦<br />\n睇班柒頭個樣又唔似做勇武<br />\n和理非香港人大撚把啦 洗撚十換一你咩<br />\n話比你班理工戇鳩仔知，你地直接殺死成班手足<br />\n千古罪人呀</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1739535/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1739535/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>今日去出元朗班傻閪死哂未？ - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>又要撩班黑社會<br />\n又唔敢出去（得幾百人）<br />\n比人打又嗌生嗌死十足廢柴mk係到叫囂<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fhehe.gif&h=ad0bad84&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fsmile.gif&h=d434394b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1373507/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1373507/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/kBN5bas.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"be9a5f8bdd76b182d4693f2bb9a537f216af4799","tid":1826923,"uid":177213,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T13:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NBo1Rmn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNBo1Rmn.png&h=195edffd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd435159f21f476d7b503837e732a71c3dcaa90c","tid":1826923,"uid":75556,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T13:56:08.000Z","msg":"蛇"},{"pid":"d7a7c63ce78132ae5396d2a58e63ce78ef24102b","tid":1826923,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T13:56:46.000Z","msg":"【重開/行動】唔想靜 就記得去參加+幫手宣傳新年行動！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1826916\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1826916</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6dd2e7dbe9c75e23928f271feaf0ae94112242cf","tid":1826923,"uid":279399,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"06395